{"tid":2244341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈萎縮46% 十月多間小店倒閉","createTime":"2020-10-15T11:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T18:41:53.000Z","uid":381081,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a447216464017699768307c5d9cc45c7f1e705","tid":2244341,"uid":381081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:51:59.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">個個雙十淨係識排龍門渣哥<br />\n黃色經濟圈唔需要小店啦？！<br />\n</span></span>  <br />\n【1026爆買日 集中火力懲罰小店！】<br />\n十月十日就舉行咗全民感謝日，當日多區嘅黃店都大排長龍，甚至有啲到tea time都坐爆，反應非常熱烈，相當成功。<br />\n<br />\n一直以嚟，好多人都會擔心，黃色經濟圈會唔會隨著運動降溫而逐漸萎縮。但10.10全民感謝日就證明咗，香港人依然用緊唔同方法去支持緊場運動。然後，好多人都會質疑幫襯黃店唔係抗爭。無錯，但唔抗爭我哋都要食飯，而食飯嘅我就一定幫襯返自己人，而唔會幫襯支持打壓自己嘅人。運動前路越來越難，但依然有人繼續出嚟遊行，依然繼續支持黃色經濟圈，其實已經係一種微小的堅持。<br />\n<br />\n雖然10.10當日唔少黃店食肆都反應熱烈，但就有啲小店就同我哋反映，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">希望大家懲罰完出名嘅黃店，都記得懲罰埋小店</span></span>。其實各區都有唔少黃色小店，如果黃色經濟圈要長久發展，我地正正就係需要更多店鋪，更多選擇。<br />\n<br />\n因此，嚟緊10月26日係黃店爆買日一周年，我哋希望支持到更多唔出名，但又默默做，默默撐住運動嘅黃色小店。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">宜家我哋收集緊想參與1026爆買日嘅黃店名單，我哋會免費提供實體文宣，同埋宣傳1026爆買日嘅海報</span></span>，期望可以一齊宣傳，做大個餅。同時都係鼓勵香港人繼續撐黃店。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎有興趣嘅黃店手足喺以下google form寫低聯絡方法：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/EEAmp8p1NPdBtKqd7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FEEAmp8p1NPdBtKqd7&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugztagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=0f9e4468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/EEAmp8p1NPdBtKqd7</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n#懲罰師 #1026爆買日 #黃色經濟圈<br />\nFB｜<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1026punishxi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1026punishxi&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugztagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=ab6fbe96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1026punishxi</a><br />\nIG📷 <a href=\"https://instagram.com/punish_xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpunish_xi&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugztagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=2e8b1266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/punish_xi</a><br />\nTG📨<a href=\"https://t.me/punish_Xi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpunish_Xi&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugztagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b1847348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/punish_Xi</a>"},{"pid":"1022a0ce2d6a5169aac8e7e5f2ab9b2fef3e22d7","tid":2244341,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:54:39.000Z","msg":"pudh"},{"pid":"22aed9c2a00b264dfa7fca9dabb09360e901a575","tid":2244341,"uid":27584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:54:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"03d4b8f0d8b5bfe26bc2fba6ecccdf5fd47449ef","tid":2244341,"uid":381081,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:56:18.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">要人要人要人要人要人要人要人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bOfKUF7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbOfKUF7.png&h=90d6897a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c3bf58a37477bbbaa6168b0f4bc91e640c7d1a27","tid":2244341,"uid":245552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"7e8e2ef79ed7968167c1af66d629675f43da7aaf","tid":2244341,"uid":261224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔起"},{"pid":"9aaed07aa3c0d9fb6edae789857b93efdcaee58c","tid":2244341,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"46%點計？"},{"pid":"d80a480533d3c8b68cea708ee18f9a468e9e6404","tid":2244341,"uid":14067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2e327df7508692e69a05098531ddcaa829e011","tid":2244341,"uid":20